OL,3,CThe soap-making workshops helping drug
OL,4,Caddicts 'get clean'
OL,6,FReport by Natalie Higgins
OL,8,FA charity is using soap-making
OL,9,Fworkshops to fund community projects
OL,10,Fthat help drug addicts to recover.
OL,12,FLeeds-based Getting Clean was formed
OL,13,Fin 2021 by volunteers with a drug or
OL,14,Falcohol dependency. It provides peer-
OL,15,Fto-peer support by getting addicts
OL,16,Finvolved in community projects.
OL,18,FAmong its initiatives are soap-making
OL,19,Fsessions that attract 10 to 20 people
OL,20,Fa session.
