OL,3,CThe soap-making workshops helping drug
OL,4,Caddicts 'get clean'
OL,6,FFounder Chris Sylvester, who has
OL,7,Fbattled addiction, said: "I kept
OL,8,Fseeing people coming back through
OL,9,Fservices more and more traumatised so
OL,10,FI thought coming in with a new
OL,11,Fapproach and with what I'd learnt in
OL,12,Fmy own recovery, I would be able to
OL,13,Fhelp others.
OL,15,F"We started out with community
OL,16,Fprojects like litter picking, repairs
OL,17,Fand recycling, but we wanted to create
OL,18,Fa product which could fund those
OL,19,Fprojects but also has value in what we
OL,20,Fdo. That's how Soap with Hope was
OL,21,Fborn."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
