OL,3,CThe soap-making workshops helping drug
OL,4,Caddicts 'get clean'
OL,6,FRoss Briggs started drinking and
OL,7,Ftaking drugs in his teens. He said the
OL,8,Fworkshops, and the support from
OL,9,Fothers, has helped him on his road to
OL,10,Frecovery.
OL,12,F"Addiction itself is very isolating
OL,13,Fand it can keep you locked in your own
OL,14,Fhead," he said. "Having the activities
OL,15,Fand sessions like this, it gives me
OL,16,Fthe chance to socialise with people.
OL,17,FFor me, it's all about building
OL,18,Fconnections."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
