OL,3,CThe soap-making workshops helping drug
OL,4,Caddicts 'get clean'
OL,6,FMoney raised through selling the soap
OL,7,Fon stalls across Leeds is used to help
OL,8,Ffund projects carried out by Getting
OL,9,FClean.
OL,11,FThe charity held a community clean-up
OL,12,Fin an area blighted by antisocial
OL,13,Fbehaviour and drug misuse. Service
OL,14,Fusers cleared the area of
OL,15,Fparaphernalia and rubbish.
OL,17,FClaire Terry, who lives on the estate,
OL,18,Fwelcomed the move after experiencing
OL,19,Fproblems in the area.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
