OL,3,CThe soap-making workshops helping drug
OL,4,Caddicts 'get clean'
OL,6,FShe said: "Me and my daughter don't go
OL,7,Fout after dark. Even during the day I
OL,8,Fkeep the doors locked. With all the
OL,9,Fantisocial behaviour that's going on,
OL,10,FI don't like to let her out at night
OL,11,Fbecause I'm scared for her."
OL,13,FFor Chris and the charity, the
OL,14,Fprojects are an opportunity to show
OL,15,Fthat people with addictions can make a
OL,16,Fpositive contribution.
OL,18,F"To see people coming in that are
OL,19,Fcoming form a background of lived
OL,20,Fexperience and giving back to the
OL,21,Fcommunity is massive", he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
